'''Pélagie Uwera''' (wavutse 1974) ni umunyapolitiki wo mu [[Rwanda]], kuva mu 2019 akaba umwe mu bagize Sena y'u [[Rwanda]], atorerwa kuba Senateri uhagarariye [[Intara y'amajyepfo|iNtara y'Amajyepfo]] <ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/senate-fresh-bid-tackle-teenage-pregnancies</ref>. <ref name="Details">[https://www.parliament.gov.rw/index.php?id=135&width=650&detailId=176 Senators Profiles: Details], parliament.gov.rw. Accessed May 5, 2020.</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Pélagie Uwera yahawe impamyabumenyi ihanitse mu bumenyi bw'imibereho  n'impamyabumenyi ihanitse mu bushakashatsi bwiterambere yakuye muri kaminuza yigenga ya [[Kigali]] <ref>https://amp.ww.en.freejournal.org/63870495/1/pelagie-uwera.html</ref>. Kuva mu 1998 kugeza 2009 yari umwarimu w'ishuri ryisumbuye<ref>ⓘ Encyclopedia - Pelagie Uwera - east african legislative assembly. Pelagi (shops-net.com)</ref>.

Kuva 2012 kugeza 2019 Uwera yari Komiseri wa komisiyo y'igihugu ishinzwe amatora mu [[Rwanda]]<ref>https://igihe.com/amakuru/u-rwanda/article/ibigo-bya-leta-birakangurirwa-kwandika-amateka-ya-jenoside-kugira-ngo</ref> . <ref name="Details">[https://www.parliament.gov.rw/index.php?id=135&width=650&detailId=176 Senators Profiles: Details], parliament.gov.rw. Accessed May 5, 2020.</ref> Umwe mu bagize Komisiyo barindwi, yabaye indorerezi ya Commonwealth mu matora rusange ya Botswana 2014 .  Muri 2018 yongeye kuba indorerezi ya Commonwealth mu matora rusange ya [[Siyera Lewone]] ya 2018 . <ref>[https://thecommonwealth.org/sites/default/files/inline/COGstatementSierraLeoneFeb2018.pdf Statement announcing the COG observers for Sierra Leone elections], February 19, 2018. Accessed May 5, 2020.</ref>

Muri 2015 yahataniraga itike y'Ishyaka Riharanira Demokarasi no Kurengera Ibidukikije nk'umukandida mu Nteko ishinga amategeko umutwe [[Afurika|w'Afurika]] y'Iburasirazuba, ariko yatsinzwe na Francois Xavier Kalinda . <ref>James Karuhanga, [https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/192473 Varsity don elected to EALA], ''[[The New Times (Rwanda)|The New Times]]'', September 12, 2015.</ref>

Mu bakandida 23 bo mu Ntara y’Amajyepfo mu matora y’Abasenateri 2019, <ref>Hudson Kuteesa, [https://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/63-candidates-vie-senate 63 candidates to viw for senate], ''[[The New Times (Rwanda)|The New Times]]'', August 17, 2019. Accessed May 5, 2020.</ref> Uwera yari umwe mu bakandida batatu batorewe guhagararira Intara. <ref>Nasra Bishumba, [https://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/men-dominate-senatorial-provincial-seats Men dominate senatorial provincial seats], ''The New Times'', September 17, 2019. Accessed May 5, 2020.</ref> Mu Kwakira 2019, yatorewe gukorera muri komite ishinzwe imyitwarire ya senateri, nk'umuyobozi wungirije wa Chrysologue Karangwa . <ref>Nasra Bishumba, [https://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/senate-sets-new-standing-committees Senate sets up new standing committees], ''The New Times'', October 30, 2019. Accessed May 5, 2020.</ref> Mu Gushyingo 2019, Uwera na senateri John Bonds Bideri batowe nta guhatanira guhagararira u [[Rwanda]] mu Nteko ishinga amategeko ya Pan-Afrika . <ref>Emmanuel Ntirenganya, [https://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/senators-uwera-bideri-represent-rwanda-pan-african-parliament Senators Uwera, Bideri to represent Rwanda in the Pan-African Parliament], ''The New Times'', November 14, 2019.</ref>

